		"description": "üöÄ Complete API collection for Member Rewards System\n\n## Quick Test Flow:\n1. **Register Member** ‚Üí Auto-saves Member ID\n2. **Verify OTP** (use `123456`) ‚Üí Auto-saves JWT Token\n3. **Add Points** ‚Üí Test points calculation (‚Çπ100 = 10 points)\n4. **View Points** ‚Üí Check accumulated points\n5. **Redeem Coupons** ‚Üí Test coupon system\n\n## Demo Credentials:\n- **OTP**: Always use `123456`\n- **Mobile**: Any 10-15 digit number (e.g., `9876543210`)\n\n## Pre-configured Coupons:\n- **‚Çπ50 Off** - Requires 500 points\n- **‚Çπ100 Off** - Requires 1000 points\n\n**Built with .NET 8 & Entity Framework Core**",
